---
title: Crispy-Skinned Chicken and Biscuits with Green Beans and Sweet Potato Mash
description: Better than grandma's biscuits? We'd say so! These DIY cheesy biscuits aren't the only star of this comforting dinner. The stick-to-your-ribs crispy chicken is sure to become a family favourite!
